TECHSTRATEGY RESEARCH

Standalone Sourcing Apps Vanish - Report
Jennifer Chew, January 2002
http://www.forrester.com/ER/Research/Report/0,1338,12180,FF.html

     Users aren't adopting today's best-of-breed sourcing apps -- instead
     they're waiting for integrated solutions from ERP, SCM, and
     product-design vendors. The result? Standalone sourcing app vendors
     fade by 2003.

