TECHNOGRAPHICS RESEARCH

Game Consoles Connect - Report
Paul Jackson, January 2002
http://www.forrester.com/ER/Research/Report/0,1338,12229,FF.html

     New consoles will add nongaming features in vain. Manufacturers
     should focus on online gaming opportunities. Broadband connectivity
     will draw 10 million console gaming households online by 2006.

